need to have a ~/bin folder in linux

need to have make, csh, gcc

need to install fftw.h(version 2.1.5) library for c
	download the package
	tar -xvzf fftw....
	./configure --enable-float --prefix=${HOME}
	make
	make install
make : works without errors in radardecode [warnings for functions]


for p2pfs data :
export DRVSB=drv.p2pfs
drv_all.sc first all
drv_scale.sc 1 1
drv_mapavg.sc 1 1 1 900 maps

drv_mapmsc.sc 1 1 1 1 [makefits does not work yet]
makefits -f -c 400 -r 1000 < 2010NY65.mapsf1 > test.fits
just the makefits (executable from rserv and asteria works)

